### A-1: rank sweep (CS-5 / D-2 / U-1 closure)

**蝠城｡悟ｮ夂ｾｩ**

CS-5 縺ｧ `rank=8` 縺ｯ "continuity hypothesis" 逡吩ｿ昴「niversal adequacy
譛ｪ荳ｻ蠑ｵ縲・oRA Land (arxiv:2405.00732) / P-Tailor (arxiv:2406.12548) 縺ｯ
universal best rank 繧・establish 縺励↑縺・Ｓank 縺御ｽ弱☆縺弱ｋ縺ｨ expressivity
荳崎ｶｳ縲・ｫ倥☆縺弱ｋ縺ｨ overfit + VRAM 豬ｪ雋ｻ縲・9-C-adopt 縺ｮ譛蛻昴・ empirical 蛻､螳・縺ｨ縺ｪ繧九・
**謗｡逕ｨ approach**

- sweep 遽・峇: `rank 竏・{4, 8, 16, 32}` (PEFT/unsloth standard powers-of-2)
- 鬆・ｺ・ G-GEAR single GPU 蛻ｶ邏・ｈ繧・sequential 蠢・医・  `rank=8` (譌｢蟄・`kant_r8_real` 繧・base 蜀榊茜逕ｨ縲∥nchor) 竊・`rank=4`
  (smaller縲〈uick fail signal) 竊・`rank=16` 竊・`rank=32` (extreme縲・  VRAM headroom 蝨ｧ霑ｫ繝ｪ繧ｹ繧ｯ)縲Ｂnchor anchored sweep 縺ｧ early continuity
  遒ｺ隱・+ 荳｡蛛ｴ extreme sample
- compute budget: 4 rank ﾃ・3 persona ﾃ・~2h training = ~24h
  (G-GEAR overnight ﾃ・3)
- **謗｡逕ｨ rank 豎ｺ螳壼渕貅・* (DA-1 縺ｧ formal 蛹・:
  1. **Vendi semantic score** (ME-10 default kernel `all-mpnet-base-v2`):
     baseline (no LoRA) 縺ｨ縺ｮ persona-discriminative gap 縺・monotonic 縺ｫ
     improve 縺励↑縺・rank 縺ｧ saturate 縺ｨ蛻､螳・竊・smallest saturated rank
  2. **Big5 ICC(C,k)** (ME-11 consistency notation): persona traits 縺ｮ
     stability ICC 竕･ 0.6 (psychometrics literature shoulder縲・     Anthropic persona vector / P-Tailor 謨ｴ蜷・ 繧呈ｺ縺溘☆譛蟆・rank
  3. **bench throughput floor**: single_lora baseline (CS-7 amendment
     2026-05-13: 34.64 tok/s) 縺ｮ 70% (= 24.25 tok/s) 繧貞・繧峨↑縺・怙螟ｧ rank
  - 3 蝓ｺ貅悶・ **intersection** (Vendi saturate floor 竕､ rank 竕､
    throughput ceiling) 繧呈治逕ｨ rank 縺ｨ縺吶ｋ縲り､・焚隧ｲ蠖捺凾縺ｯ VRAM 蜉ｹ邇・怙螟ｧ
    (= smaller rank) 繧帝∈縺ｶ
- **譽・唆 rank archival**: `data/lora/m9-c-adopt/archive/rank_{4,8,16,32}/
  {persona}/` 縺ｫ蜈ｨ sweep 邨先棡 (adapter weights + Tier B JSONL + bench
  JSONL) 繧・retain縲∝ｾ檎ｶ夂皮ｩｶ baseline 縺ｨ縺励※菫晄戟縲Ｑroduction loader 縺ｯ
  謗｡逕ｨ rank 縺ｮ縺ｿ load

**莉｣譖ｿ譯医→譽・唆逅・罰**

- **binary search** (rank=8 竊・16 竊・12 竊・14): 荳ｭ髢・rank 縺ｯ LoRA standard
  practice 縺ｧ uncommon縲￣EFT/unsloth default 縺・powers-of-2 縺ｮ縺ｿ縲・  literature comparison 縺悟峅髮｣
- **parallel sweep**: single GPU 縺ｧ荳榊庄閭ｽ縲［ulti-GPU 縺ｯ scope 螟・- **rank=64 蜷ｫ繧**: VRAM 荳崎ｶｳ繝ｪ繧ｹ繧ｯ鬮・(CS-4 estimate ~8.7GB base縲・  rank=64 縺ｧ +200MB adapter + activation 蠅怜刈)縲…ost-benefit poor
- **rank=8 蝗ｺ螳・* (empirical sweep skip): CS-5 逡吩ｿ昴′ adopt phase 縺ｧ
  closure 蠢・ｦ√‘mpirical 譛ｪ遒ｺ隱阪・縺ｾ縺ｾ production wiring 縺ｯ CS-5 縺ｮ
  re-open 譚｡莉ｶ繧呈悴貅縺溘☆

**risk / unknowns**

