    `SGLangChatClient.load_adapter()` 逶ｴ蜿ｩ縺阪〒蜿ｯ閭ｽ (= dev path 遒ｺ菫・縲・    縺溘□縺・`inference/server.py` 邨檎罰縺ｯ block
