    evaluation_epoch=false` 縺ｮ training enforcement 縺ｯ **蠢・・*縲《ilent skip
    縺ｯ contamination prevention 驕募渚
  - 1000 example 縺ｯ ERRE-Sandbox spike scope 縺ｫ蟇ｾ縺吶ｋ **operational SLO**
    (literature constant 縺ｧ縺ｯ縺ｪ縺・，S-3 縺ｧ operational decision 縺ｨ縺励※險倬鹸)
- **譽・唆**:
