## CS-4 窶・VRAM budget: gradient_checkpointing + double quant + memory logging (Codex MEDIUM-3)

- **豎ｺ螳・*:
  - `gradient_checkpointing=True` 蠑ｷ蛻ｶ
  - `bnb_4bit_use_double_quant=True` (nested quantization)
  - `batch_size=1`, `gradient_accumulation_steps=8`, `seq_length=2048`
    (initial config)
  - `nvidia-smi` peak memory logging 繧・training entry point 縺ｫ邨・ｾｼ
  - VRAM budget (螳滓ｸｬ蜑・estimate):

    | 鬆・岼 | VRAM |
    |---|---|
    | Qwen3-8B NF4 + double quant | ~5.0GB |
    | LoRA rank=8 adapter | ~50MB |
    | gradient (gc=True) | ~1.5GB |
    | optimizer state (LoRA params only) | ~0.2GB |
    | activation (seq=2048, batch=1) | ~1.5GB |
    | buffer | ~0.5GB |
    | **蜷郁ｨ・* | **~8.7GB** |
    | **headroom (16GB - 8.7)** | **~7.3GB** |
- **譬ｹ諡**:
  - Codex MEDIUM-3: VRAM estimate is plausible but optimistic縲∝ｮ滓ｸｬ蠢・・  - HF benchmark (https://huggingface.co/blog/4bit-transformers-bitsandbytes):
    7B 8-bit + GC at seq1024 竊・OOM縲・-bit NF4 + GC 竊・passes
  - TRL doc (https://huggingface.co/docs/trl/reducing_memory_usage):
    gradient_checkpointing 縺ｯ memory-positive縲…ompute-negative (training
    time +20-30%)
  - double quant 縺ｧ base model VRAM ~10% 蜑頑ｸ・(M9-B DB1 alternatives 蜿り・
- **譽・唆**:
  - `gradient_checkpointing=False` (8-bit 縺ｧ繧・seq1024 縺ｧ OOM縲，odex MEDIUM-3
    quote)
  - `bnb_4bit_use_double_quant=False` (10% headroom 謳榊､ｱ縲［arginal 鬆伜沺縺ｧ
    諢丞袖縺ｪ縺・
  - `batch_size=2` (gradient memory ~2x縲”eadroom 荳崎ｶｳ繝ｪ繧ｹ繧ｯ)
  - `seq_length=4096` (activation memory ~2x縲（nitial 縺ｧ縺ｯ risky)
- **蠖ｱ髻ｿ**:
  - `src/erre_sandbox/training/train_kant_lora.py` 縺ｮ training config 縺ｫ
    荳願ｨ伜崋螳・  - peak memory > 12GB 隕ｳ貂ｬ譎ゅ・ CS-4 re-open (螳滓ｸｬ蛟､縺ｧ revised config 襍ｷ逾ｨ)
  - Phase K ﾎｲ 縺ｧ螳滓ｸｬ蛟､繧・CS-4 縺ｮ amendment 縺ｫ霑ｽ險・- **re-open 譚｡莉ｶ**:
  - 螳滓ｸｬ peak memory > 12GB 竊・batch / seq / accumulation 蜀崎ｪｿ謨ｴ
  - CUDA fragmentation 縺ｧ long-context generation 縺御ｸ榊ｮ牙ｮ・竊・seq_length 邵ｮ蟆・  - SGLang serving 譎ゅ・ base + 3 active adapters 縺・VRAM budget 繧定ｶ・℃ 竊・    `--max-loaded-loras` 邵ｮ蟆・
