## CS-7 窶・N=3 collapse 讀懷・: SGLang `bench_serving` + 4 trigger condition (Codex HIGH-4)

- **豎ｺ螳・*:
  - benchmark tool: SGLang `bench_serving` harness (https://docs.sglang.io/
    developer_guide/bench_serving)
  - baselines (3 遞ｮ螳滓ｸｬ):
    - no-LoRA (base Qwen3-8B縲～--enable-lora` 縺ｪ縺・
    - single-LoRA Kant only
