    --max-loaded-loras 3 --max-concurrency 3`
  - metrics: TTFT p50/p95/p99 / ITL / e2e latency / output tokens/s /
    HTTP error rate / queue wait (if available)
  - **collapse trigger (any one of)**:
    - p95 e2e > 2x single-LoRA baseline
    - output tok/s < 70% baseline
    - adapter-misrouting (Kant prompt 竊・Nietzsche/mock adapter response縲・      sentinel 縺ｧ讀懷・)
    - request timeout (1 莉ｶ縺ｧ繧・
- **譬ｹ諡**:
  - Codex HIGH-4: "no collapse" 縺ｯ subjective縲｜enchmark contract 蠢・・  - SGLang `bench_serving` 縺ｯ throughput / TTFT / ITL / e2e latency / request
    rate / max concurrency / JSONL 蜃ｺ蜉帙ｒ documented support
  - 2x p95 縺ｨ 70% throughput 縺ｯ ERRE-Sandbox operational SLO (literature
    constant 縺ｧ縺ｯ縺ｪ縺・，odex 謗ｨ螂ｨ benchmark 縺ｧ baseline 縺ｨ逶ｸ蟇ｾ豈碑ｼ・
