    縺悟酔遲我ｻ･荳翫ｒ support)
  - "collapse 縺ｪ縺・ 縺ｮ subjective 蛻､螳・(HIGH-4 縺ｧ discarded)
  - p95 1.5x / output 80% 遲・lenient threshold (production headroom 荳崎ｶｳ)
- **蠖ｱ髻ｿ**:
  - Phase K ﾎｲ G-GEAR 螳溯ｵｰ縺ｧ `bench_serving` 繧・3 baseline 縺ｧ螳溯｡・  - 邨先棡 (JSONL) 繧・`data/eval/spike/m9-c-spike-bench/` 縺ｫ菫晏ｭ・(譁ｰ隕・path)
