## ME-2 窶・DuckDB snapshot semantics (G-GEAR write 竊・Mac read-only) (Codex MEDIUM-2)

- **豎ｺ螳・*: G-GEAR 縺・DuckDB file 縺ｮ蜚ｯ荳 writer縲｀ac 縺ｯ read-only consumer縲・  rsync 縺ｯ莉･荳九・ protocol 縺ｧ螳溯｡・
  1. **G-GEAR 蛛ｴ**: 謗｡蜿悶そ繝・す繝ｧ繝ｳ邨ゆｺ・凾縺ｫ `con.execute("CHECKPOINT")` 竊・     `con.close()` 縺ｧ WAL 繧・main file 縺ｫ flush
