## ME-11 窶・ICC McGraw-Wong notation + dual-consumer split (Codex P4a HIGH-2)

- **豎ｺ螳・*:
  - **notation 邨ｱ荳**: McGraw & Wong (1996) 陦ｨ險倥ＡICC(A,1)` = absolute agreement
    single rater縲～ICC(A,k)` = absolute agreement k-rater average縲～ICC(C,1)` =
    consistency single縲～ICC(C,k)` = consistency k-rater average
  - **dual-consumer split**:
    - **ME-1 reliability fallback trigger**: `ICC(C,k)` consistency primary 繧呈治逕ｨ縲・      threshold 縺ｯ ME-1 譌｢豎ｺ縺ｮ 0.6 (point) / 0.5 (lower CI) 繧堤ｶ咏ｶ夐←逕ｨ (Koo-Li
      2016 cutoff 縺ｮ譬ｹ諡縺ｯ consistency)
    - **DB9 drift/adoption gate**: `ICC(A,1)` absolute agreement primary 繧呈治逕ｨ縲・      level shift = drift signal 縺ｨ縺励※謇ｱ縺・・*ME-1 threshold 豬∫畑遖∵ｭ｢**縲．B9 逕ｨ
      cutoff 縺ｯ P4b 縺ｧ persona-conditional 縺ｫ calibrate
  - `Big5ICCResult` 縺ｫ荳｡ consumer 縺ｮ蛟､繧剃ｽｵ險・(consistency + agreement縲∥verage +
    single)縲～me1_fallback_fire` flag 縺ｯ consistency 縺ｮ縺ｿ蜿ら・
  - degenerate case (identical 蜈ｨ constant 蝗樒ｭ・竊・ANOVA 0/0): **諢丞峙逧・special
    case** 縺ｨ縺励※ `icc_*=1.0, degenerate=True, fallback_fire=False` 繧定ｿ斐☆
- **譬ｹ諡**:
  - Codex P4a HIGH-2: "ICC(2,k) consistency" 縺ｯ notation 豺ｷ蝨ｨ (Shrout-Fleiss vs
    McGraw-Wong vs Koo-Li)縲［erge-safe 縺ｧ縺ｯ縺ｪ縺・  - Koo & Li 2016 (https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/27330520/): ICC 縺ｯ model / type
    / definition 縺ｮ驕ｸ謚槭′蠢・ｦ√，I 縺ｧ interpret
  - drift detection 縺ｮ諢丞袖隲・ systematic offset 繧定ｨｱ螳ｹ縺吶ｋ consistency 縺ｧ縺ｯ LoRA
    persona drift 縺梧黒縺ｾ繧峨↑縺・∥bsolute agreement 縺・construct valid
  - degenerate ANOVA: 蜷御ｸ row 縺ｧ縺ｯ between-subject SS = 0 竊・0/0縲∵э蝗ｳ逧・special
    case 蛹悶′蠢・ｦ・- **譽・唆**:
  - 蜊倅ｸ ICC formula primary 蛹・(v1/v2 譯・ 竊・荳｡ consumer 縺ｮ諢丞袖隲悶′逡ｰ縺ｪ繧九◆繧∽ｸ榊庄
  - ME-1 threshold 0.6/0.5 繧・ICC(A,1) 縺ｫ繧・literally 豬∫畑 竊・calibration 縺ｪ縺励〒縺ｯ
    threshold 螯･蠖捺ｧ縺梧昭繧峨＄
  - degenerate 繧・ANOVA 縺九ｉ閾ｪ辟ｶ縺ｫ蜃ｺ蜉帙＆縺帙ｋ 竊・0/0 縺ｧ NaN 蛹悶！CC=1.0 繧・    assumption 縺ｧ縺ｯ縺ｪ縺・explicit special case 縺ｫ縺吶∋縺・- **蠖ｱ髻ｿ**:
  - `tier_b/big5_icc.py` 縺ｮ `Big5ICCResult` dataclass 縺ｫ consistency + agreement
    荳｡ surfaced
  - `test_big5_icc.py` 縺ｧ offset-sensitivity test 霑ｽ蜉 (consistency 荳榊､峨∥greement
    螟牙喧)
  - `decisions.md` ME-1 縺ｮ child ADR 縺ｨ縺励※險倬鹸縲｀E-1 threshold 縺ｯ consistency 蟆ら畑
    縺ｨ譏手ｨ・- **re-open 譚｡莉ｶ**:
