## DB6 窶・Evaluation epoch 蛻・屬: Run-level flag + 迚ｩ逅・partition + sidecar (HIGH-4 邨ｱ蜷・ + 鬆ｻ蠎ｦ policy (MEDIUM-4)

- **豎ｺ螳・*:
  - `evaluation_epoch: bool` 繧・Run config 蠢・亥喧縲．efault `False`
  - Parquet partition 縺ｧ迚ｩ逅・・髮｢ (`raw_dialog/evaluation_epoch=*/`)
  - sidecar metrics table 繧ょ酔 partition 讒矩
  - **鬆ｻ蠎ｦ policy**:
    - **Tier A**: per turn (cheap, ~50ms total)
    - **Tier B**: per 100 turns (Vendi / IPIP-NEO / Big5 ICC)
    - **Tier C**: nightly offline batch (Prometheus 2 / G-Eval / FANToM-adapted) 窶・autonomous run 蛛懈ｭ｢譎ゅ・縺ｿ螳溯｡・- **譬ｹ諡**:
  - codex HIGH-4 + MEDIUM-4: Tier C judge LLM (Prometheus 2 8x7B class) 縺ｯ qwen3:8b agent
    縺ｨ VRAM contention縲∝酔譎ょｮ溯｡御ｸ榊庄
  - 迚ｩ逅・partition 縺ｯ HIGH-4 隗｣豸医・ core mechanism
