     縺ｮ `connect_training_view()` / `connect_analysis_view()` 縺ｮ荳｡ entry 縺ｧ wrapper enforced)
  - **NFS / SMB / iCloud 蜈ｱ譛・fs 邨檎罰縺ｯ遖∵ｭ｢** (DuckDB doc 縺・file lock 隴ｦ蜻・
