            options: Extra OpenAI-compatible request keys (``max_tokens``,
                ``stop``, 窶ｦ). ``temperature`` / ``top_p`` /
                ``repetition_penalty`` here are silently overridden by
                ``sampling`` (mirrors the Ollama adapter's clamp invariant).
